I am a new writing blog that is dedicated to the wonderful world of Boku No Hero Academia or My Hero Academia! I recently fell in love with this show and many of you might recognize my writing style from @theredpaladude. That is me as well!

question: I hate Mineta too lol I always either write him off or make him the antagonist in my fanfics. My biggest problem with him is the perviness isn't balanced out, like yeah lots of other anime charas are pervs, but they have other amazing traits to balance it. Mineta is just... dull, his quirk is boring as hell, he looks awful design-wise, his voice is annoying; he's just really frustrating and I wish they hadn't even included him in BNHA :/
answer: it also sucks that despite how useless he is in the series, he’s in all the promotional stuff for some reason like??? a piece of stale bread could contribute more than him and be more deserving of promotional merch.
